      <h3>100% Satisfaction Guarantee</h3>
      <p>We get it—finding the perfect skin tint can be tricky. That’s why we make it effortless.</p>
      <p><strong>Try it, wear it, love it</strong>—and if it’s not the perfect match, we’ve got you covered with our <strong>30-Day Money-Back Guarantee.</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="guarantee-image">
      <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0964/4130/3378/files/gempages_534627086933951483-1f2932c0-3d4e-435b-8ffd-90a7cdd12713_1024x_6d594f0d-d19e-43c2-b4be-a679837000d4.webp?v=1747525583" alt="Guarantee Models">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
